WEBVTT

00:00:00.863 --> 00:00:03.852
I am so excited to be here.

00:00:03.876 --> 00:00:06.680
Everything in America
is so much bigger than in Europe.

00:00:06.704 --> 00:00:08.676
Look at me -- I am huge!

00:00:08.700 --> 00:00:10.361
(Laughter)

00:00:10.385 --> 00:00:11.535
It's fantastic!

00:00:11.559 --> 00:00:14.839
And TED Talks -- TED Talks
are where everybody has great ideas.

00:00:14.863 --> 00:00:18.260
So the question is: Where do
those great ideas come from?

00:00:18.284 --> 00:00:20.630
Well, it's a little bit of debate,

00:00:20.654 --> 00:00:23.192
but it's generally reckoned
that the average person --

00:00:23.216 --> 00:00:24.374
that's me --

00:00:24.398 --> 00:00:26.932
has about 50,000 thoughts a day.

00:00:26.956 --> 00:00:28.114
Which is a lot,

00:00:28.138 --> 00:00:30.964
until you realize that 95 percent of them